<% tickets = @order.tickets.reject(&:canceled_at?) %>
<% unassigned = tickets.reject(&:assigned?) %>
Your order <%= @order.code %>

Hello <%= @order.buyer_name %>,

Here is the permanent link to your order. Bookmark it - it is where you download
your tickets and tax invoice, and where you name your attendees:

<%= order_url(@order.code) %>
<% if unassigned.any? %>
<%= pluralize(unassigned.size, "ticket") %> still <%= unassigned.one? ? "has" : "have" %> nobody named on <%= unassigned.one? ? "it" : "them" %>.
<% else %>
All <%= pluralize(tickets.size, "ticket") %> already have an attendee. If anything needs
correcting, use the links below.
<% end %>
One link per ticket - send an attendee their own link and they fill in their own
name, dietary needs, T-shirt size and childcare:
<%= render "order_mailer/claim_links", order: @order, formats: [ :text ] %>
See you in Pune.
